Hidden on the edge of a very popular park. Muggles all the time. Must be careful. Park open dawn to dusk. Bring your dog on a leash. Thanks to Korat for the idea. Difficulty is for muggles and the cache.
Congratulations to bpp_picnic for FTF and Deb3day for STF.
